      <Property Name="Name">StaticTextControl1</Property>
      <Property Name="Size">439, 65</Property>
      <Property Name="Location">20, 55</Property>
      <Property Name="BackColor">HighlightText</Property>
      <Property Name="Text">This configuration presents a typical use case in which the different VIO I/O cards 
(VIO1008, VIO1804, VIO2004, VIO4028) stimulate and analyze an electronic circuit.

A small demo hardware ('VIO System Sample DUT') is needed 
to setup a complete test environment.</Property>
